{"lemma":"إِرْسال","slug":"إِرْسال","root":"ر.س.ل","root_slug":"ر-س-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-س-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n15487"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A5%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%84"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of أَرْسَلَ (ʔarsala) (form IV)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sending, dispatching"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of أَرْسَلَ (ʔarsala)."},"ipa":["/ʔir.saːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n15487","headword_ar":"اـِرْسَالٌ","root":"rsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sending."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, KL, &c.) Thus is explained"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irosaAlu A@ll~`hi A^anobiyaA='ahu","text_ar":"اـِرْسَالُ ا@للّٰهِ اَنْبِيَا=ءَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God's sending his prophets."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Th, TA.) You say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arosalotu fulaAnFA fiY risaAlapK","text_ar":"اَرْسَلْتُ فُلَانًا فِى رِسَالَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sent such a one with a message."},{"kind":"text","text":"(PS.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arsl A_ilayohi rasuwlFA","text_ar":"ارسل اـِلَيْهِ رَسُولًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, Msb *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sent to him a message,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a letter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a messenger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  [The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sending forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"starting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a horse for a race: the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discharging"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing; as, for instance, an arrow from a bow; and water, or the like, from a vessel &c. in which it was confined: the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"launching forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"a ship or boat;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"letting"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"go; letting"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"take its course:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"setting loose"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"free; letting loose; loosing, unbinding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"liberating."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arsl Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"ارسل الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He set loose"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"free,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arosalotu AlT~aAy^ira mino yadiY","text_ar":"اَرْسَلْتُ الطَّايِرَ مِنْ يَدِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I let go,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"let loose, the bird from my hand."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And [hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arsl AlHuruwfa","text_ar":"ارسل الحُرُوفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He uttered the letters"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rtl","text_ar":"رتل"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arsl AlginaA='a","text_ar":"ارسل الغِنَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He uttered the song; he sang"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arsl AlA_iqaAmapa","text_ar":"ارسل الاـِقَامَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He chanted the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AqAmp","text_ar":"اقامة"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drj","text_ar":"درج"},{"kind":"text","text":". [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adoraja","text_ar":"اَدْرَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arsl Ealayohi lisaAnahu","text_ar":"ارسل عَلَيْهِ لِسَانَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He let loose his tongue against him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brd","text_ar":"برد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arsl AlkalaAma","text_ar":"ارسل الكَلَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made the speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"language, to be unrestricted."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [In like manner,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irosaAlN","text_ar":"اـِرْسَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing, such as property, and a legacy,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"absolute,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unrestricted."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) ―         -b3-  [The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"letting down, letting fall,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making to hang down,"},{"kind":"text","text":"the hair &c. You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arslhu","text_ar":"ارسلهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arslhu mino A^aEolaY A_ilaY A^asofala","text_ar":"ارسلهُ مِنْ اَعْلَى اـِلَى اَسْفَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He let it down,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowered it."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)  The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaving, leaving alone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"neglecting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) a thing. (M.) [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arslhu Eano yadihi","text_ar":"ارسلهُ عَنْ يَدِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He left, forsook,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deserted, him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he abstained from,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1082},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"neglected, aiding him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assisting him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  Also The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making to have dominion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"authority, and power; making to have,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exercise, absolute dominion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sovereignty"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rule,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"absolute superiority of power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"giving power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"superior power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) Hence, in the Kur [xix. 86],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arosalonaA Al$~ayaATiyna EalaY","text_ar":"اَرْسَلْنَا الشَّيَاطِينَ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlkaAfiriyna taw^uz~uhumo A^az~FA","text_ar":"الكَافِرِينَ تَوُزُّهُمْ اَزًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We have made the devils to have dominion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"over the unbelievers, inciting them strongly"},{"kind":"text","text":"to acts of disobedience; or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"we have appointed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared, the devils for the unbelievers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of their unbelief; like as is said in the same [xliii. 35],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqay~iDo lahu $ayoTaAnFA","text_ar":"نُقَيِّضْ لَهُ شَيْطَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[“ We will appoint, or prepare, for him a devil ” as an associate]: this is the preferred explanation: [or it may be well rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"we have sent the devils against the unbelievers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] some say that the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"we have left the devils to do as they please with the unbelievers, not withholding them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preserving them, from acceptance from them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, M.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArslwA","text_ar":"ارسلوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"risolN","text_ar":"رِسْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They had milk in their cattle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their milk became much;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rs~lwA","text_ar":"رسّلوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarosiylN","text_ar":"تَرْسِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or the latter signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their milk and drink became much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also [from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasalN","text_ar":"رَسَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They became possessors of herds"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flocks."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K. *)"}],"source_refs":["S","MA","M","K"]}]}}